= Bold and Italic Text

Text formatting rules for bold and italic emphasis.

== Bold Text

This paragraph contains *bold text* within it.

This paragraph has **unconstrained bold** text in the middle.

== Italic Text

This paragraph contains _italic text_ within it.

This paragraph has __unconstrained italic__ text in the middle.

== Combined Formatting

This paragraph has *_bold italic_* text.

This paragraph has **__bold italic__** unconstrained text.

== Bold and Italic Together

This is *bold* and this is _italic_ in the same paragraph.

This is **bold** and this is __italic__ unconstrained.

== Bold with Other Formatting

This paragraph has *bold* and `monospaced` text together.

This paragraph has *bold* and a https://example.com[link].

== Italic with Other Formatting

This paragraph has _italic_ and `monospaced` text together.

This paragraph has _italic_ and a https://example.com[link].

== Nested Formatting

This paragraph has *bold with _italic inside_* it.

This paragraph has _italic with *bold inside*_ it.

== Edge Cases

*Bold at start* of paragraph.

_Bold at end_ of paragraph.

*Single asterisk* and _single underscore_ work too.

